[[瑞士|瑞士]][[蘇黎世|蘇黎世]]的'''車站大街'''是歐洲最長的購物大道，也是世界上最昂貴的購物大道之一，與[[紐約|紐約]][[第五大道|第五大道]]齊名<ref>[http://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/business/Bahnhofstrasse_rents_at_record_high.html?cid=32083766 Bahnhofstrasse rents at record high] swissinfo.ch. Retrieved on 2012-02-07</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cushmanwakefield.com/en/news/2016/11/new-yorks-upper-5th-av-remains-worlds-most-expensive-retail-street/|title=New York's Upper 5th Av remains world's most expensive retail street|website=www.cushmanwakefield.com}}</ref>。
